ally-grounded way, and we demonstrate the effectiveness of our\napproach on both synthetic and empirical networks.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 5 Apr 2018 17:23:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 6 Dec 2018 22:16:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-12-10"}
