ower-law liquid is the likely cause of the superconducting dome in\nthe cuprates.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 5 Apr 2018 18:00:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 20 Oct 2018 11:55:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-11-07"}
