ity\npredictions, as well as computational tools for content producers and marketers\nto allocate resources for promotion campaigns.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 6 Apr 2018 01:12:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 10 Apr 2018 21:41:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-04-12"}
