 provides a frame for monomorphisms obtained\npreviously, and which have been described in low degrees.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 6 Apr 2018 12:18:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 17 Sep 2020 17:25:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-18"}
